<p>The Fontenelle Forest area neighborhoods often feature larger lots with less shading, ideal for ground-mounted solar systems or expansive rooftop installations. Near Offutt Air Force Base, homes may have specific architectural considerations, but the stable community provides excellent conditions for long-term solar investments. Western Bellevue developments often feature newer construction with modern electrical systems that easily accommodate solar installations, while eastern areas closer to the Missouri River may require additional consideration for humidity control in HVAC system selection.</p>

